cassandra-utils
===============

  A tiny utils for cassandra db to backup sstables easily


dump
====

    % thor backup:dump
Argument Error: needs both <KEYSPACE> and <BACKUP_DIR> arguments.

For Example:

    thor backup:dump Keyspace1 20100514

This will execute following commands.
Try again like that, or simply copy and paste.

sstable2json /var/lib/cassandra/data/Keyspace1/Standard2-28-Data.db > 20100514/Standard2-28-Data.db.json
sstable2json /var/lib/cassandra/data/Keyspace1/Standard2-30-Data.db > 20100514/Standard2-30-Data.db.json
...


